<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A nuom ngei ie Isu muon hih,
 Amah thu bang a pawm hih;
 Amah thutiem a kingak hih,
 &quot;Lalpa gen dan&quot; hetna tawh.

[V2]
 Isu, Isu, Amah ka muong!
 Amah ka hechien deuhdeuh!
 Isu, Isu, lulpen Isu!
 Zahngaihna di'n Amah muon!

[V3]
 2. Aw, a nuom hi Isu muon hih,
 A thienna thisan muon chuh;
 Ginna mawltak a kidieh di'n,
 Damna, thienna thisan ah.

[V4]
 3. Ahi, anuom ngei Isu muon,
 Gitloh, kei deih beina di'n;
 Hinna, chawlhna, nawpna, muonna,
 Isu kawm a lak mai chuh!

[V5]
 4. Nang ka hun muong a ka kipak,
 Isu lul, Hukdampa, Guol;
 Ka kawm a Nang na um ka hei,
 Tawp chana ei umpih ding.</lyrics>
<title>'TIS SO SWEET TO TRUST IN JESUS</title>
</song>